# Setup

This project requires a GCC compiler and the Protocol Buffers code generation tools.

---

## ðŸ”§ Install Protobuf Compiler

Install the `protoc` tool by following the official instructions:  
ðŸ‘‰ [https://grpc.io/docs/protoc-installation/](https://grpc.io/docs/protoc-installation/)

Alternatively, you can download a pre-built binary from:  
ðŸ‘‰ [https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf/releases](https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf/releases)  
Place the extracted binary somewhere in your `$PATH`.

---

## ðŸ“¦ Install Go Protobuf Codegen Tools

Install the following tools using `go install`:

```bash
go install google.golang.org/protobuf/cmd/protoc-gen-go@latest
go install google.golang.org/grpc/cmd/protoc-gen-go-grpc@latest
